&lt;li&gt;Experience: 5–8 years of relevant experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in commissions, sales compensation, finance, accounting, revenue operations, sales operations, or business analytics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills with the ability to review large datasets, identify variances, and resolve discrepancies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced Microsoft Excel skills, including lookups, pivot tables, formulas, and data validation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail, accuracy, organization, and follow-through.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to communicate clearly with sales representatives, managers, and cross-functional partners.&lt;/li&gt;
