&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Vectra we seek to make the world a safer and fairer place, build a culture we&#39;re proud of and leverage AI to its full potential to do good, We do these things by leveraging our values of&lt;strong&gt; Integrity&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Teamwork&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Customer First&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here is how we define our values:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Integrity:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;our-values-grid-right_cell&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;paragraph font-size-18px font-color-grey-400 is-16px-mobile&quot;&gt;Integrity is our foundation. It drives every decision we make and every action we take. We believe in doing what is right, even when no one is watching. We prioritize honesty, transparency and fairness, earning your trust every step of the way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;our-values-grid-right_cell&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Teamwork:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;container is-1234px-max-width is-position-relative&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;w-layout-grid grid is-2col&quot;&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;w-node-_90101658-0552-edd5-f627-9c44a0bff752-b56e7906&quot; class=&quot;our-values-grid-right&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;our-values-grid-right_cell&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;paragraph font-size-18px font-color-grey-400 is-16px-mobile&quot;&gt;We value teamwork that is focused, efficient and drama-free. We respect and challenge each other to do the best work we can. The collaborative culture we&#39;ve cultivated means we can accomplish extraordinary feats.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;paragraph font-size-18px font-color-grey-400 is-16px-mobile&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer First:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For over a decade, we’ve been obsessed with creating what security analysts and SOC leaders have repeatedly told us is most critical: creating the most accurate attack signal. We have teams of security researchers, data scientists and software engineers who are laser focused on perfecting our signal, improving it every day. Our company is committed to providing the best attack signal on the planet, providing an easy-to-use platform and providing white-glove, proactive and responsive service along with shared accountability to make the lives of our customers easier.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;paragraph font-size-18px font-color-grey-400 is-16px-mobile&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
